Class PluginHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.common.collect.ForwardingObject
      • com.google.common.collect.ForwardingCollection<E>
        • com.google.common.collect.ForwardingList<Plugin>
          • net.tridentsdk.server.plugin.PluginHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<Plugin>, Collection<Plugin>, List<Plugin>, Plugins, Registry<Plugin>

    public class PluginHandler
extends com.google.common.collect.ForwardingList<Plugin>
implements Plugins
    Handles server plugins, loading and unloading, class management, and lifecycle management for plugins

    To access this handler, use this code: 

    
     PluginHandler handler = Registered.plugins();

    Since:
    0.3-alpha-DP
    Author:
    The TridentSDK Team
